  {
    "content": "In the previous sections, we systematically analysed the\nevolving landscape of AI-driven cyberattacks, covering their\ntypes, current trends in defensive AI mitigation strategies,\nmotivations, and societal impacts. In this section we delve\ndeeper into the implications of these findings. We synthe-\nsise the emergent themes to highlight their theoretical and\npractical significance. We critically engage with the collec-\ntive insights to assess their bearing on current cybersecu-\nrity frameworks, ethical considerations, and policy direc-\ntives. Additionally, we identify gaps in the existing body\nof knowledge, thereby highlighting compelling avenues\nfor future research. Through this integrative discourse, we\naim to contribute a nuanced understanding of the complex\ninterplay between AI and cybersecurity, with the intent of\nTable 8   Motivations of AI-empowered cyber attackers\nAuthor\nMotivation for carrying out cyberattack\n[6]\nEconomic incentives; Exploitation of AI vulnerabilities; Opportunity due to insider threats\n[27]\nExploitation of AI vulnerabilities\n[28]\nEconomic motivations; Competitive espionage; Psychological manipulation\n[10]\nTechnological advancements in AI tools; Elevated attack success rate\n[3]\nAutomate attacks, making them more efficient and scalable; Exploit AI vulnerabilities, such as adversarial\nattacks; Develop adaptive and stealthy capabilities\n[4]\nAutomated and efficient attacks; Stealthy and evasive capability of AI; Exploiting AI vulnerabilities; Make\nmoney through theft or ransom; Gain information through espionage; Cause physical or psychological\ndamage for sabotage, terrorism, fame, or revenge; Reach another targeted organisation; obtain foothold\non the organisation as an asset for later use\n[5]\nTechnological advancements of AI tools; Accessibility and sophistication of AI tools; Economic Incentives\n[16]\nLeveraging AI's learning and adaptability\n[94]\nEconomic incentive; psychological impact; Political manipulation\n[14]\nFinancial gain; Increased efficiency and profitability; National interests\n[88]\nSophistication through AI; Geostrategic motivations to further national interests;",
