    "content": "AI and Ethics (2025) 5:883–910\ncyber threats. Therefore, we now turn our attention to the\nmotivations behind AI-driven cyberattacks.",
    "metadata": {
      "page_num": 20,
      "section": "Artificial intelligence (AI) cybersecurity dimensions: a comprehensive > 5.2  \u0007Trends in defensive AI mitigation strategies > approach to cybersecurity in the age of AI.",
