    "content": "to provide timely information about malicious activities. DM\ntechniques extract the hidden features to differentiate between\nnormal and malicious activities and are successfully adopted\nresulting in legacy cyber security solutions in the market such\nas network-level and host-level firewalls, antivirus software,\nIntrusion Detection Systems (IDSs), and Intrusion Protection\nSystems (IPSs). However, such solutions are effective in\ndetecting only the known malicious activities and fail to detect\nnew types of malicious activities associated with Industry",
